public class QVTOTransformationJob
extends java.lang.Object
implements de.uka.ipd.sdq.workflow.IJob, de.uka.ipd.sdq.workflow.IBlackboardInteractingJob<de.uka.ipd.sdq.workflow.mdsd.blackboard.MDSDBlackboard>

Configures and executes a QVT-O transformation job. Most important, this includes the configuration of source and target models as well as the transformation script. Minor configuration settings include the configuration of the QVT-O logger. Originally, the classes from de.uka.ipd.sdq.workflow.mdsd.emf.qvto were intended to realize the above described functionality. However, their inability to specify unexisting target models where no root element is already included led to the implementation of this class. Future work may resolve this issue; optimally by adding the functionality to the de.uka.ipd.sdq.workflow.mdsd.emf.qvto classes.

Version:
0.1
Author:
